{"tid":2205792,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦 Notes vs 手寫 Notes","createTime":"2020-09-17T05:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T00:49:56.000Z","uid":168930,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a30f58b13eeaef9e12682fbbc1e7d73dc4b34dac","tid":2205792,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"之前一向手寫Notes <br />\n但發現寫完之後極少睇返 因為啲字唔靚<br />\n今年做咗電腦Notes<br />\n我發現工整一致既字幾易入腦<br />\n唔洗諗返我手寫字係寫咩<br />\n再轉換返意思<br />\n減少一層用腦空間<br />\n<br />\n同埋電腦Notes可以 直接搵到內容<br />\n唔洗一頁一頁睇<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fed3024a0b3b5ed62a1317e0d3e08c3a7a663a","tid":2205792,"uid":71508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"Ipad is the best"},{"pid":"1263ceadd0b7df607d46c1d9d488960f51f2e976","tid":2205792,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"Use LaTeX<br />\n打得開心，睇得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f651276ee77845885eb93834d3e235e12a38582","tid":2205792,"uid":118247,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"反而我調返轉<br />\n以前手寫notes我會mark好多箭嘴、符號<br />\n一睇返會記得當時情況點解會咁mark<br />\n溫起上嚟易入腦啲"},{"pid":"13d1db84e84fa65a95cbc1a4f951a52223a01984","tid":2205792,"uid":80785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1263ceadd0b7df607d46c1d9d488960f51f2e976","tid":2205792,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:25:58.000Z","msg":"Use LaTeX<br />\n打得開心，睇得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"Ching latex用開咩editor"},{"pid":"4c04fa5d6df6d524584ea95bea479f77e9cdf08c","tid":2205792,"uid":230641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T05:31:11.000Z","msg":"之前有免費quota一定用紙抄<br />\n而家屋企定大學 曬墨曬紙要好多錢<br />\n下個sem 一定轉iPad"},{"pi