b2b","tid":2205792,"uid":299187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:43:59.000Z","msg":"電子手寫+打<br />\n手寫notes好似記圖像去記嘢，用嚟mark重點<br />\n打字會用唔同字體，又係利用圖像去幫助記憶<br />\n有研究講過 d字愈難睇，你花多啲時間去睇會印象深刻d"},{"pid":"75801490099b6ece4922aeb0481846ef216e2999","tid":2205792,"uid":142712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:51:22.000Z","msg":"手寫notes<br />\n唔想睇mon，耐咗眼會痛<br />\n自己寫嘅嘢容易記<br />\n唔會睇返自己啲notes"},{"pid":"52de70bdc4ad1acb3e37d35ad1c1d9609cea4b09","tid":2205792,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"兩樣加埋 用手寫落平板電腦"},{"pid":"6b1d0fa2a7a3a9c390be30165b52e02f81b1e13f","tid":2205792,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T20:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8554668484a2c4c1f238b2094ea7c75577b5ff","tid":2205792,"uid":358248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T00:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}